lead_paragraph: Senator Charles Schumer, the third-ranking Democrat in the U.S. Senate, said on Tuesday he expects President Barack Obama to pick a "mainstream nominee" for the Supreme Court.

headline.main: Senator Schumer Expects 'Mainstream Nominee' for Supreme Court
